menu "Cicada MQTT Credentials"

config CICADA_PROVISION_FROM_EMBEDDED
    bool "Provision MQTT client cert/key from embedded files if missing"
    default y
    help
        When enabled, firmware embeds device.crt/device.key and will write them
        into NVS on first boot if missing. Use this for factory provisioning builds.
        For release builds, disable this so private key is NOT present in firmware.

endmenu
